keyMappings:
map H previousTab
map L nextTab
map \ passNextKey
map F LinkHints.activateModeToOpenInNewForegroundTab
map <c-g> LinkHints.activateModeWithQueue
map ; passNextKey normal
map <tab> Vomnibar.activateTabSelection
map - goBack
map _ goForward
map <c-6> visitPreviousTab

unmap J
unmap K
unmap t
unmap T
unmap U
unmap R
searchEngines:
w: https://www.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Special:Search&search=%s Wikipedia
g: https://github.com/search?q=%s&type=Code Github
